nd visit, a strange and powerful lightning storm touches down.","genre_ids":[12,53,878],"popularity":8.8816,"vote_count":8977,"poster_path":"/6Biy7R9LfumYshur3YKhpj56MpB.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-28","vote_average":6.531,"backdrop_path":"/bInicBgSHfQiWLbnRT5jxw9Grvm.jpg","original_title":"War of the Worlds","original_language":"en"},{"id":77,"adult":false,"title":"Memento","video":false,"overview":"Leonard Shelby is tracking down the man who raped and murdered his wife. The difficulty of locating his wife's killer, however, is compounded by the fact that he suffers from a rare, untreatable form of short-term memory loss. Although he can recall details of life before his accident, Leonard cannot remember what happened fifteen minutes ago, where he's going, or why.","genre_ids":[9648,53],"popularity":9.4126,"vote_count":15927,"poster_path":"/fKTPH2WvH8nHTXeBYBVhawtRqtR.jpg","release_date":"2000-10-11","vote_average":8.176,"backdrop_path":"/7Wev9JMo6R5XAfz2KDvXb7oPMmy.jpg","original_title":"Memento","original_language":"en"},{"id":78,"adult":false,"title":"Blade Runner","video":false,"overview":"In the smog-choked dystopian Los Angeles of 2019, blade runner Rick Deckard is called out of retirement to terminate a quartet of replicants who have escaped to Earth seeking their creator for a way to extend their short life spans.","genre_ids":[878,18,53],"popularity":11.9762,"vote_count":14713,"poster_path":"/63N9uy8nd9j7Eog2axPQ8lbr3Wj.jpg","release_date":"1982-06-25","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/hJ5R9d6QuH3tzr8L8neZZTuzNXm.jpg","original_title":"Blade Runner","original_language":"en"},{"id":270931,"adult":false,"title":"Out of the Shadows","video":false,"overview":"A U.S. Embassy worker is helped by an Interpol agent to prove herself innocent of a murder in the Greek isles.","genre_ids":[10770,53],"popularity":0.3987,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/k9HzsKYVPWkQ8nsjg7zSnJ4oF1O.jpg","release_date":"1988-09-02","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":