s the case progresses and the Church's dark secrets are revealed, Vail finds that what appeared a simple case takes on a darker, more dangerous aspect.","genre_ids":[80,18,9648,53],"popularity":5.739,"vote_count":3788,"poster_path":"/qJf2TzE8nRTFbFMPJNW6c8mI0KU.jpg","release_date":"1996-03-06","vote_average":7.656,"backdrop_path":"/dZM71rHXh3Oo3WZlw8YpMMsoVB5.jpg","original_title":"Primal Fear","original_language":"en"},{"id":1598,"adult":false,"title":"Cape Fear","video":false,"overview":"Sam Bowden is a small-town corporate attorney. Max Cady is a tattooed, cigar-smoking, Bible-quoting, psychotic rapist. What do they have in common? 14 years ago, Sam was a public defender assigned to Max Cady's rape trial, and he made a serious error: he hid a document from his illiterate client that could have gotten him acquitted. Now, the cagey Cady has been released, and he intends to teach Sam Bowden and his family a thing or two about loss.","genre_ids":[18,80,53],"popularity":3.6632,"vote_count":3776,"poster_path":"/ws4mrtndzgSH5QGCamOFAgilr2R.jpg","release_date":"1991-11-13","vote_average":7.255,"backdrop_path":"/ntgpger7OwFNlEldxuvvFHDKzjW.jpg","original_title":"Cape Fear","original_language":"en"},{"id":273187,"adult":false,"title":"The Scarehouse","video":false,"overview":"When two friends open a Halloween fun house on Devil's Night it is all fun and games until their former sorority sisters begin to arrive. These six sisters are confronted by their past as the night spins out of control.","genre_ids":[53,27],"popularity":0.3391,"vote_count":55,"poster_path":"/dE6VEAOTvJOu0ER6nkSkfJKxCG2.jpg","release_date":"2014-09-13","vote_average":4.4,"backdrop_path":"/n6JPhgmFzdYbozKJSa0JTaOmHEO.jpg","original_title":"The Scarehouse","original_language":"en"},{"id":1672,"adult":false,"title":"The Professional","video":false,"overview":"French secret service agent Josselin Beaumont is dispatched to take down African warlord N'Jala. But when his assignment is canceled, he's shocked to learn that his government is surrendering him to local authorities. He is given a mock trial and sentenced to 20 years of hard labor. But Beaumont escapes from prison and vows not only to avenge himself against his betrayers but also to finish his original assignment.","genre_ids":[28,12,53],"popularity":1.6992,"vote_count":574,"poster_path":"/dhAZ8T0tTlTNw3D7Cn8wc87sk1w.jpg","release_date":"1981-10-21","vote_average":7.185,"backdrop_path":"/mQsMFca19fZsLKMc6x5FjwncTYh.jpg","original_title":"Le Professionnel","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1679,"adult":false,"title":"Godzilla Raids Again","video":false,"overview":"Two fishing scout pilots make a horrifying discovery when they encounter a second Godzilla alongside a new monster named Anguirus. Without the weapon that killed the original, authorities attempt to lure Godzilla away from the mainland. But Anguirus soon arrives and the two monsters make their way towards Osaka as Japan braces for tragedy.","genre_ids":[878,27,28],"popularity":1.2982,"vote_count":322,"poster_path":"/ipU1exHwS04FhdonFXsliOKrr2a.jpg","release_date":"1955-04-24","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/xbKFQCZNK14gp9k6cFCwgp2OCtU.jpg","original_title":"ゴジラの逆襲","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1573,"adult":false,"title":"Die Hard 2","video":false,"overview":"One year after his heroics in Los Angeles, John McClane is an off-duty cop who is the wrong guy in the wrong place at the wrong time. On a snowy Christmas Eve, as he waits for his wife's plane to land at Washington Dulles International Airport, terrorists take over the air traffic control system in a plot to free a South American army general and drug smuggler being flown into the US to face drug charges. It's now up to McClane to take on the terrorists, while coping with an inept airport police chief, an uncooperative anti-terrorist squad, and the life of his wife and everyone else trapped in planes circling overhead.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":6.7639,"vote_count":6273,"poster_path":"/